definition: to arrange/to line up/file/series/(in data tables) column/(Tw) row
to lift/to hold up/to cite/to enumerate/to act/to raise/to choose/to elect/act/move/deed

sentences.english: Some cases of explainations of medical classics by professor Xu Ping are presented.
sentences.chinese: 文中列舉了幾則徐平教授解析“醫經”的案例。

sentences.english: Can anyone else list for me the six kingdoms of the scientific classification system?
sentences.chinese: 還有誰能給我列舉出科學分類系統的六大領域？

sentences.english: Set out to do something you don’t know how.
sentences.chinese: 列舉一些你不知道該從何做起的事情。

sentences.english: Some preventive measures of skidding damage used on foreign aero-engines are listed.
sentences.chinese: 列舉了國外一些發動機中防止滑蹭損傷採用的措施。

sentences.english: I'm going to give you some facts and figures about left-handedness.
sentences.chinese: 我要列舉一些事實和數據關於左撇子。

sentences.english: Finally, typical applications of retroreflectors and retroreflecting materials are given.
sentences.chinese: 最後列舉了逆反光材料的應用。

sentences.english: This is a partial list at best.
sentences.chinese: 這裏列舉的充其量只是一小部分。

sentences.english: When did you begin to do professional translation Please describe your translation experience in detail.
sentences.chinese: 您從何時開始從事專業翻譯請詳細列舉您的翻譯經驗。

sentences.english: Below, I list some important ways of circumventing the aforementioned problems.
sentences.chinese: 下面我列舉一些能夠避免上述問題的方法。

sentences.english: But who can describe the thousand means of extinguishing the moccoletto?
sentences.chinese: 但誰能列舉出那成千上萬種熄滅長生燭的方法呢？

sentences.english: The Journal also pointed to other recent players in the divestiture game.
sentences.chinese: 該報同時還列舉了剝離遊戲中的其他一些玩家。

sentences.english: Let me enumerate many flaws in your hypothesis.
sentences.chinese: 讓我列舉你前提中的許多謬誤。

sentences.english: Enumerates some phenomena of the design mechanism unaccommodated to building energy efficiency in China.
sentences.chinese: 列舉了我國設計機制不適應建築節能需求的現象。

sentences.english: Let me give some brief indications of their subject.
sentences.chinese: 讓我列舉一些簡單的關於這些主題的提示。

sentences.english: The allowable duration of abnormal frequency operation for large turbo-generator sets provided by the main manufactories on the world is listed.
sentences.chinese: 列舉了世界各國生產的大機組頻率異常運行允許時間。

sentences.english: Enumerators only allow reading the data in the collection.
sentences.chinese: 列舉值只允許讀取集合中的資料。
